[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    136[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Issue:** The architecture shows AWS Glue pulling data from the billing system via Direct Connect or VPN. The recipe doesn't discuss whether the Glue job's security group restricts egress to only the billing system's IP/port. In a multi-tenant VPC environment, an overly permissive security group could allow the Glue job to reach other systems on the corporate network.
